Record clade metadata in results table

Source: R/recordAncestor.R
recordClades.Rd

Add new focalClade and focalColor columns to a results table, for use in some plots.

Usage

recordClades(df, clades)

Arguments

df

A results data frame created with the extractValues() function.

clades

A FocalCladeList object.

Note

As MRCA information is needed; the function will run recordAncestor() when it did not find it.

See also

Other Focal clade functions: eog(), focalClade(), recordAncestor(), subMatrix(), subTree(), visualizeTree()

Author

Charles Plessy

Examples

recordClades(Halo_DF, Halo_FocalClades)
